### animated plot

cf <- df %>% group_by(year) %>% summarise(av_upper = mean(max_t))

p3 <- ggplot(cf,mapping = aes(x = year, y = av_upper), frame = year)

anim <- p3 +
  geom_point() +
  transition_manual(year, cumulative = TRUE) +
  ggtitle("The year is: {frame +1882}")
anim
